{"about_the_game":"<strong>Villages\u2122</strong> is a game that combines interesting mechanics from many other sandbox games. <br>It aims to let People face a variety of gameplay and scenario by conducting a few basic rules.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749820/extras/StoreContentBanner.png?t=1729912573\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Economy, the game's world will have limited resources so ones will not get the same resources and amount. People will then form an economy by using the trading system in the game.</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Manufacturing, from hand-crafted to factory-made you can make a product with different tiers. Each tier varies in cost and benefit and makes it dynamic to the whole economy.</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Construction, differ from a traditional sandbox game. Villages\u2122 will let you construct a building as if in real life, by using construction sites, construction tools, and vehicles.</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Skill-Based, People can choose their skill to advance but with limited skill points. So you must balance your skill branches and benefit from them. Everyone will depend on other People's abilities and form their own society.</ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Other Planned Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Clan and Company System</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Law Enforcement</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Vehicles</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Weapons</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Stores</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Industries</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Warzone</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_strike\">Fishing</span></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_strike\">Hunting</span></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Go Vegan</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Farming(Permakultur)</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Animal Sanctuary</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Forest Ranger Job</ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729912573","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749820/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729912573","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749820/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729912573","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749820/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729912573","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<strong>Villages\u2122</strong> is a game that combines interesting mechanics from many other sandbox games. <br>It aims to let People face a variety of gameplay and scenario by conducting a few basic rules.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749820/extras/StoreContentBanner.png?t=1729912573\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Economy, the game's world will have limited resources so ones will not get the same resources and amount. People will then form an economy by using the trading system in the game.</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Manufacturing, from hand-crafted to factory-made you can make a product with different tiers. Each tier varies in cost and benefit and makes it dynamic to the whole economy.</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Construction, differ from a traditional sandbox game. Villages\u2122 will let you construct a building as if in real life, by using construction sites, construction tools, and vehicles.</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Skill-Based, People can choose their skill to advance but with limited skill points. So you must balance your skill branches and benefit from them. Every